name: NekoLib
author: justinsanjp
description:
NekoLib is a mod that contains many open source libraries & self-made scripts where modding becomes easier and better. through this mod it is possible to develop extensive mods.

these Lib. are included:
1. [Lodash](https://github.com/lodash/lodash)  
2. [Day.js](https://github.com/iamkun/dayjs)  
3. [Anime.js](https://github.com/juliangarnier/anime)  
4. [Chart.js](https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js)  
5. [Simple.js](https://github.com/simplejs/simple)  
6. [EventEmitter3](https://github.com/primus/eventemitter3)  
7. [Vite](https://github.com/vitejs/vite)  
8. [Console.js](https://github.com/pyrsmk/console.js)  
9. [Chance.js](https://github.com/chancejs/chancejs)  
10. [Howler.js](https://github.com/goldfire/howler.js)  
11. [JSZip](https://github.com/Stuk/jszip)  
12. [FileSaver.js](https://github.com/eligrey/FileSaver.js)
